title: KCR backs Rahul’s surgical strike proof demand, Sarma hit back with ‘Gandhi family loyalty jibe’ - Hindustan Times
content:
1. KCR backs Rahul’s surgical strike proof demand, Sarma hit back with ‘Gandhi family loyalty jibe’  Hindustan Times
  2. KCR Demands Proof Of Surgical Strikes, Says 'Nothing Wrong With Asking For Proof'  Republic World
  3. Army should get credit for surgical strikes, not BJP: Telangana CM KCR  India Today
  4. Even today I`m asking for proof of surgical strike: Telangana CM K Chandrashekhar Rao  Zee News
  5. Nothing wrong with Rahul Gandhi demanding proof of surgical strikes, I also want: Telangana CM KCR  Times Now
  6. View Full coverage on Google News
description: “There is nothing wrong with Rahul Gandhi asking for proof of the surgical strikes. Even now I am asking. Let the Government of India show. It is their responsibility. There are apprehensions among people,” Telangana chief minister K Chandrashekhar Rao said on Sunday.
